SOCCER - GUATEMALA - TRINIDAD / TOBAGO DRAW . Guatemala and Trinidad and Tobago played to a 1 - 1 draw in a CONCACAF World Cup qualifying game on Sunday . Carlos Ramirez scored for Guatemala in the 24th minute , and Jerren Nixon got the equaliser for Trinidad and Tobago in the 39th minute . A capacity crowd of 20 , 000 watched the game . 
